quote.p:
Considering that resolving of the conflict in
Korea is an important step towards the restoration of world peace and
friendly relations among nations;

“Reaffirming its objective for the establishment
                            of a united, independent and democratic government in the sovereign
                            state of Korea;

list.item:
“3. As soon as the cease-fire has become effective, representatives of _____ should meet to make recommendations for
“(a) Rehabilitation and restoration of normal conditions in Korea;
“(b) The establishment of a united, independent and democratic government in the sovereign state of Korea.”
